public static final class CameraServiceGrpc.CameraServiceBlockingStub extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractBlockingStub<CameraServiceGrpc.CameraServiceBlockingStub>
A stub to allow clients to do synchronous rpc calls to service CameraService. 
 A CameraService services all cameras associated with a robot
